snippet.title: Etrian Odyssey Nexus | Trailer #1
snippet.description: Etrian Odyssey Nexus launches for Nintendo 3DS™ on February 5, 2019! As the final Etrian installment on 3DS, it’s only natural that we’ve gone all out incorporating all of the best aspects throughout the entire series, including iconic characters, 19 playable classes, and more labyrinths than any other Etrian title. Get your first look at Etrian Odyssey Nexus in our first official trailer.
